== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2013年4月，[[夢工廠動畫公司|夢工廠動畫公司]]宣佈製作《[[古魯家族|古魯家族]]》續集，[[克里斯·桑德斯|克里斯·桑德斯]]和{{le|科克·德密科|Kirk DeMicco}}回歸執導<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=103135 |title=The Croods 2 in the Works at DreamWorks Animation |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2013-04-17 |accessdate=2018-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006150729/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=103135 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年6月12日，宣佈續集將於2017年11月3日上映<ref name=":0">{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=119483 |title=Dates Set for Madagascar 4, The Croods 2, Puss in Boots 2, Captain Underpants, and Hitman |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2014-06-12 |accessdate=2018-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006124318/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=119483 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年8月21日，該片延期至2017年12月22日上映<ref name=CSShiftsTwo>{{cite web|title=DreamWorks Animation Shifts Two Sequels Back Slightly|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=122167|publisher=ComingSoon.net|accessdate=2018-10-07|date=2014-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824140252/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=122167|archive-date=2014-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年8月23日，據報導《[[樂高玩電影|樂高玩電影]]》和《[[尖叫旅社|尖叫旅社]]》的聯合編劇凱文·哈格曼和丹·哈格曼被聘來重寫劇本<ref name="DeadlineHagemanBrothers">{{cite web|last1=Busch|first1=Anita|title=DreamWorks Animation's 'Croods 2' Gets Rewrite With Hageman Brothers|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dreamworks-animation-croods-2-kevin-dan-hageman-brothers-1201807624/|website=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=2018-10-07|date=2016-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007073655/https://deadline.com/2016/08/dreamworks-animation-croods-2-kevin-dan-hageman-brothers-1201807624/|archive-date=2018-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年11月11日，夢工廠宣佈取消製作《古魯家族2》<ref name="VarietyTakenOff">{{cite news|last1=Rainey|first1=James|title=DreamWorks Animation and Universal Kill ‘Croods 2’ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/dreamworks-animation-universal-kill-croods-2-sequel-1201916453/|accessdate=2018-10-07|work=Variety|date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190103134655/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/dreamworks-animation-universal-kill-croods-2-sequel-1201916453/|archive-date=2019-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，在2017年9月，夢工廠和[[環球影業|環球影業]]透露該片已重新投入製作，並計劃於2020年9月18日上映，但德密科因執導[[索尼動畫|索尼動畫]]電影《[[VIVO金曲歌王|VIVO金曲歌王]]》不會回歸續集<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sony-pictures-animation-unveils-varied-upcoming-slate-300392965.html|title=Sony Pictures Animation Unveils Varied Upcoming Slate|agency=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|publisher=Sony Pictures Animation|date=2017-01-18|accessdate=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006114708/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/sony-pictures-animation-unveils-varied-upcoming-slate-300392965.html|archive-date=2018-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年10月，喬爾·克勞佛將接替桑德斯成為該片的導演，而{{le|馬克·史威夫特與達米安·香農|Mark Swift and Damian Shannon|馬克·史威夫特}}將擔任製片人<ref>{{cite news|last=Giardina|first=Carolyn|title='Croods 2' Finds Its Director (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/croods-2-finds-director-1050172|date=2017-10-18|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621195504/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/croods-2-finds-director-1050172|archive-date=2018-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
2013年9月，確認[[尼可拉斯·凱吉|尼可拉斯·凱吉]]、[[艾瑪·史東|艾瑪·史東]]和[[萊恩·雷諾斯|萊恩·雷諾斯]]回歸聲演咕嚕（Grug）、一妹（Eep）和阿蓋（Guy）<ref>{{cite web|title=Nicolas Cage, Ryan Reynolds and Emma Stone Confirmed for The Croods 2|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=108718|date=2013-09-09|work=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]]|publisher=[[CraveOnline|CraveOnline]]|accessdate=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422033120/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=108718|archive-date=2014-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月21日，[[萊絲莉·曼恩|萊絲莉·曼恩]]和[[凱特·丹寧絲|凱特·丹寧絲]]加盟並聲演希旺·郝野人（Hope Betterman）和棠棠·郝野人（Dawn Betterman），而{{le|凱薩琳·齊勒|Catherine Keener}}和{{le|克拉克·達克|Clark Duke}}回歸聲演娥姐（Ugga）和坦克（Thunk）<ref name="THRMannDennings">{{cite web|title=Leslie Mann, Kat Dennings Joining 'Croods 2' (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/leslie-mann-kat-dennings-joining-797398|author=Borys Kit|date=2015-05-21|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=([[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]])|accessdate=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007073743/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/leslie-mann-kat-dennings-joining-797398|archive-date=2018-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年9月，確認首集的配音員將回歸聲演各自的角色<ref name="CroodsReturn2">{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|date=2017-09-19|title=‘Croods 2’ Revived as Animated Sequel and Jason Blum’s ‘Spooky Jack’ Get Release Dates|publisher=Variety|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/croods-2-spooky-jack-release-dates-1202563635/|access-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604034547/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/croods-2-spooky-jack-release-dates-1202563635/|archive-date=2019-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Amidi|first=Amid|date=2017-09-19|title=Dreamworks Confirms ‘The Croods’ Sequel Is Back On, And Announces ‘Spooky Jack’|publisher=[[Cartoon_Brew|Cartoon Brew]]|url=http://www.cartoonbrew.com/feature-film/dreamworks-confirms-making-croods-sequel-announces-spooky-jack-153604.html|accessdate=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513011655/https://www.cartoonbrew.com/feature-film/dreamworks-confirms-making-croods-sequel-announces-spooky-jack-153604.html|archive-date=2019-05-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年10月，[[彼得·汀克萊傑|彼得·汀克萊傑]]加盟並聲演角色菲爾·郝野人（Phil Betterman）<ref>{{cite news|last1=N'Duka|first1=Amanda|last2=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|title=Peter Dinklage Joins Voice Cast Of ‘The Croods 2’|url=https://deadline.com/2018/10/peter-dinklage-the-croods-2-dreamworks-1202476719/|date=2018-10-05|work=Deadline|accessdate=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006123256/https://deadline.com/2018/10/peter-dinklage-the-croods-2-dreamworks-1202476719/|archive-date=2018-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年10月，夢工廠透露[[凱莉·瑪麗·陳|凱莉·瑪麗·陳]]將取替丹寧絲成為棠棠的配音員<ref>{{cite|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/kelly-marie-tran-joins-voice-cast-croods-sequel-1250499|title=Kelly Marie Tran Joins Voice Cast of 'Croods' Sequel|last=Galuppo|first=Mia|publisher=Hollywood Reporter|date=2019-10-29|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214130307/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/kelly-marie-tran-joins-voice-cast-croods-sequel-1250499|archive-date=2019-12-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《古魯家族：新石代》由[[環球影業|環球影業]]於2020年11月25日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|title=‘The Croods 2’: Universal Moves DreamWorks Animation Pic Into Thanksgiving Frame|url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/the-croods-2-universal-thanksgiving-release-dreamworks-animation-pic-amc-trolls-world-tour-1234578084/|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-09-16|accessdate=2020-09-17|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118045351/https://deadline.com/2020/09/the-croods-2-universal-thanksgiving-release-dreamworks-animation-pic-amc-trolls-world-tour-1234578084/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然後在聖誕節發行[[VOD|VOD]]。此前，上映日期曾定於2017年11月3日、2017年12月22日、2020年9月18日和2020年12月23日<ref name=":0" /><ref name="CSShiftsTwo" /><ref name="CroodsReturn">{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|date=2017-09-19|title=‘Croods 2’ Revived as Animated Sequel and Jason Blum’s ‘Spooky Jack’ Get Release Dates|publisher=Variety|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/croods-2-spooky-jack-release-dates-1202563635/|access-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604034547/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/croods-2-spooky-jack-release-dates-1202563635/|archive-date=2019-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|title='Sing 2’ To Croon Summer 2021; ‘The Croods 2’ Moves To Holiday Season 2020|url=https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|accessdate=2019-04-12|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828024514/https://deadline.com/2019/04/sing-2-croods-2-release-date-changes-1202594951/|archive-date=2019-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

